\c 10
\s Jehovha acharopafadza Judha naIsiraeri
\p
\v 1 Kumbirai kuna Jehovha mvura nenguva yemvura yokupedzisira, achavapa mvura inonaya kwazvo, mumwe nomumwe ave nezvinomera mumunda.
\p
\v 2 Nokuti terafimi dzakataura zvisina maturo, vawuki vakaona nhema, vakaudza vanhu kurota kwenhema, vanovaraidza pasina; saka vanozviindira samakwai, vanotambudzika nokushaiwa mufudzi.
\p
\v 3 Kutsamwa kwangu kwakamukira vafudzi, ndicharova mutungamiriri; nokuti Jehovha wehondo wakashanyira boka rake, iyo imba yaJudha, achavaita sebhiza rake rakanaka pakurwa.
\v 4 Kwaari kuchabva ibwe rekona, kwaari mbambo, kwaari uta hwehondo, kwaari vabati vose pamwechete.
\v 5 Vachava semhare dzinotsika vavengi vadzo pasi pakurwa mumatope enzira dzomumusha; vacharwa nokuti Jehovha anavo; vatasvi vamabhiza vachanyadziswa.
\v 6 "Ndichasimbisa imba yaJudha, ndichaponesa imba yaJosefa, nokuvadzoserazve, nokuti ndichavanzwira nyasha; vachava savanhu vasina kurashwa neni; nokuti ndini Jehovha Mwari wavo, ndichavanzwa.
\v 7 VaEfuremu vachava semhare, mwoyo yavo ichafara savanhu vakabatwa newaini; zvirokwazvo vana vavo vachazviona, vakafara; mwoyo yavo ichafara munaJehovha.
\p
\v 8 "Ndichavaridzira muridzo, ndivaunganidze; nokuti ndakavadzikinura; vachawanda sezvavaiwanda kare.
\v 9 Ndichavakusha pakati pendudzi dzavanhu; vachandirangarira kunyika dziri kure; vachararama pamwechete navana vavo, vakadzoka.
\v 10 Ndichavadzosazve panyika ndichavaunganidza ndichavabvisa paAsiria; ndichavasvitsa kunyika yeGireadhi neRebhanoni; vachashaiwa pokugara.
\v 11 ACkkinka nomugungwa rokutambudzika, acharova mafungu mugungwa, pakadzika pose muNairi pachapwa; kuzvikudza kweAsira kuchaderedzwa, tsvimbo youshe yeIjipiti ichabviswa.
\v 12 Ndichavasimbisa muna Jehovha, vachafamba muzita rangu," ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
